<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Pip Edwards has decided to revamp her look with a fresh new haircut. </p>

<p>The 40-year-old has swapped her shoulder length lob for a much shorter 'do. </p>

<p>On Tuesday, the P.E Nation designer debuted her new hairstyle on Instagram as she flaunted her fit physique in tight activewear during a Pilates class.</p>

<p>Fresh cut: On Tuesday Pip Edwards (pictured) debuted her new haircut on Instagram as she flaunted her fit physique in activewear</p>

<p>In the image, Pip stood on tip toes in a pair of orange exercise leggings and a black crop top from her own line, which revealed her super toned torso. </p>

<p>The mother-of-one was smiling as she tipped her head to the side. </p>

<p>The blonde, who is current'y dating former cricket captain Michael Clarke, captioned the post: 'Happy'. </p>

<p>Before and after: Pip revamped her look by swapping her shoulder length lob (left) for a much shorter 'do (right)</p>

<p>Pip also shared a series of images of her strenuous fluidform Pilates workout to her Instagram Story. </p>

<p>In one image, Pip was balancing on her forearms and her feet were in straps on a reformer machine.  </p>

<p>Another image showed Pip hanging upside down with both feet in the air while she gripped the bar above her. </p>

<p>Working up a sweat: Pip also shared a series of images of her strenuous fluidform Pilates workout to her Instagram Story</p>

<p>Don't let go! One image showed Pip hanging upside down with both feet strapped in the air while she gripped the bar above her</p>

<p>Last week Pip also turned heads by wearing a pair of nude-coloured leggings that made her appear naked at first glance.</p>

<p>Instagram fans did a double take as she uploaded a photo of herself modelling the optical illusion tights inside her Pilates studio.</p>

<p>Posing next to a reformer machine, a pouty-looking Pip wrote in the caption: 'Hands down my most favourite place to be ... the Pilates studio.'</p>

